Section 1150.2. A. There is hereby re-created until July 1,
22 2026, in accordance with the Oklahoma Sunset Law, the Child Death
Review Board within the Oklahoma Commission on Children and Youth.
23 The Board shall have the power and duty to:
24
Req. No. 17604 Page 14

1 1. Conduct case reviews of deaths and near deaths of children
in this state;
